Account related
Azure login az login
Azure list accounts az account list
Azure change account az account set --subscription 25ec5bae-####-####-##########
Show current account az account show
ACR related
Login az acr login --name <acr-name> --resource-group <rg01> --subscription <subs>
List repositories az acr repository list --name <acr-name> --output table
N.B. push a tag with :latest also. It's not automatic.
